'''MILL-247-EEs''' were types of [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoid]] industrial [[Droid/Legends|droids]]. They were [[Sentience/Legends|sentient]] and were used for emergency work on freighters. They were equipped with wrist-mounted [[Blaster/Legends|blasters]] and a knowledge of cooking, engineering, and medical arts. [[Millie]] was a MILL-247-EE.

